{"tid":1246821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"11點半轉圍警察總部，點睇？","createTime":"2019-06-21T01:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T04:00:41.000Z","uid":121048,"like":407,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"0cb3495f4029687e7630833d8f4263566c0978be","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:34:37.000Z","msg":"坐咗係政總兩三個鐘，一路聽到有人講：「齋坐唔知做乜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周不時見有人走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依架我地完全冇目標冇方向，淨係話要儲人，但又冇話儲到幾點。俾你等到3點，啲人都收得皮啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等夠人又點？又係政總齋坐？<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議轉圍警察總部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一嚟禮賓府條路難行，唔適合幾百人衝上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二嚟起碼警察總部會有犬係到，到時包圍嗰到，你叫口號也好、播片都好，至少會有一個目標，俾警犬一啲壓力。更重要嘅係，我地有野可以做，唔淨係係政總到鳩坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次開po，有錯屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家一齊入嚟討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9d47b0341c991f80c1c3b06d10da5cc1f8a86f","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b77ad8231d806870d147a1fc376b0d91ece7e4c","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:36:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7f9b6421671d71840795871ee626ac1d712cb8b","tid":1246821,"uid":254371,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"6f9d47b0341c991f80c1c3b06d10da5cc1f8a86f","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:37:42.000Z","msg"