\">https://lih.kg/1246617</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[終於有信比大家!] 請廣傳 唔好再比林鄭 黑警 醫管局fake 9外國傳媒，心好累，我連通兩晚頂搵資訊比大家的<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244090</a><br />\n</strong></span></span></blockquote>credit to 月娥奔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aebb5109f2a03ed44c1b599bccb76afc9f1afdd","tid":1246821,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:39:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bcfe43dd65c0fe963d26af46e44d94f17c7ee31","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f7f9b6421671d71840795871ee626ac1d712cb8b","tid":1246821,"uid":254371,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"6f9d47b0341c991f80c1c3b06d10da5cc1f8a86f","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:37:42.000Z","msg":"得千五人圍候撚呀！公安五分鐘清走你啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"圍但唔一定衝，警犬夠膽先清人走，師出無名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd28ca2d9dd64db9e3a92477ab193f484aaf7a06","tid":1246821,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:40:05.000Z","msg":"走左都可以返黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdc61c322202b1430ab633352c7e0879df30243","tid":1246821,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8aebb5109f2a03ed44c1b599bccb76afc9f1afdd","tid":1246821,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"628fa5b0ef9b72e8afb45796ae6983744a58b2ac","tid":1246821,"uid":135867,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"quote":{"pid":"2bc511d10da78bdfba0ca3f9ffd5c807dbdaf2e0","tid":1246821,"uid":258598,"like":16,"dislike":148,"score":-1