l.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b4f708975f2881f3141a12431f2f316be1973a","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:48:51.000Z","msg":"唔好再齋坐，磨滅自己友嘅士氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推"},{"pid":"d457d8e46fa10fe5ad513f2a149f44955a89a1b7","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:51:58.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6998372f32464b5373da9102d165c7bfd2c55bfa","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:54:30.000Z","msg":"大家入嚟討論下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8859b08139568dcc3903f787cc153b31596c095d","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:55:56.000Z","msg":"有冇人有建議啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2b338b917dd58daac7989df30b437f0a5d650c","tid":1246821,"uid":189112,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7點已經嚟到，坐到而家，有啲似漫無目的咁，已經聽到有人話「今日比人水咗出嚟」之類既說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係話一定要衝，但最起碼有個目標，唔好令人覺得出嚟齋坐坐完返屋企咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc7f5218c3a38ca27df8cdfd81ffdf883b99f5c","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:59:45.000Z","msg":"香港人點樣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爭氣少少好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9d3b07c461ed3712e3f1259c3702b314f9f937","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:01:53.000Z","msg":"3點先衝太遲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大把人7點就準時到咗，依架先嚟話3點衝，咁點解我地唔3點先到啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfb007da37cd381bdb965e38f6310ad72ca8f0c","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:02:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"191b56c0d8de8c20016b50422a63c23028df8305","tid":1246821,"uid":189112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:02:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a7cb1b9400824914b143fed4df9ac0df4cd801d","tid":1246821,"uid":134002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:03:31.000Z","msg":"出緊黎 係咪都係去左政總先？"},{"pid":"e0380756e4c4b71bf31a549675d241e8fb83e911","tid":1246821,"uid":121048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7a7cb1b9400824914b143fed4df9ac0df4cd801d","tid":1246821,"uid":134002,"like":0,"dislike"