<br />\n行動派應該應該圍住警察總部，要求警察交代之前唔肯出示委任證的人的身份。<br />\n文宣組應該向外國聲稱已經有有公安 / 解放軍混入香港警察打壓示威者，保安局 / 警方至今無法證實有關人士身份。<br />\n我們需要比外界知道「有中國公安、解放軍假冒香港警察打示威者」。<br />\n之前好多片段都影到好多黑背心的人唔肯show委任證，有依啲片段已經構成合理懷疑。<br />\n證實佢地唔係公安的責任喺政府身上。證明的責任喺政府身上，而唔係喺市民身上。<br />\n<br />\n就算今次不了了之，未來十幾廿年都要一直對外聲稱「有中國公安、解放軍假冒香港警察打示威者」。"},{"pid":"70d0e993a82da2e1b33bba9938a10d9cc7888f34","tid":1246821,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:29:28.000Z","msg":"一齊撚狗"},{"pid":"91fab203573e093cd9b05385446a29ec108b3051","tid":1246821,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:29:30.000Z","msg":"圍緊狗總"},{"pid":"c92db740d7c144ccb29aa975271847bdba274299","tid":1246821,"uid":254371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"Gophone 唔好變膠"},{"pid":"cc5bc8e92c36ef76a32fb9e8f2b7ca18ba6e0d4d","tid":1246821,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:33:05.000Z","msg":"到左"},{"pid":"39dfea1c229afaef468dce22fdcf5503c88bb013","tid":1246821,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c05cc5481f2795b1d8a3670df05edd32716615","tid":1246821,"uid":256002,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"07a3d2937fbbb2c7734b33591a43892c9ad326e1","tid":1246821,"uid":263857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bc511d10da78bdfba0ca3f9ffd5c807dbdaf2e0","tid":1246821,"uid":258598,"like":16,"dislike":148,"score":-132,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:38:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:50:19.000Z","msg":"屌你 分化夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:05:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:34:16.000Z","msg":"hi，前線狗仔，你又出嚟"},{"pid":"1f75896795ee521358e4057bf3cca8fba59ad6c5","tid":1246821,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:34:23.000Z","msg":"等左成朝，難得霸到條路，又係咁放車行<br />\n<br /